00:18:29.606 --> 00:18:47.715
Incoming livestream: So we program to implement, like, security logic to forbid dangerous action sequences. We have state-aware session tracking, which means we have an orchestrator that maintains finite state machine, tracking risk level of contacts, and then we can dynamically restrict downstream capabilities based on data origin.

